procedural

The goal of procedural is to provide a set of tools for working with the 2024 ICD-10-PCS procedure classification system.

📦 Installation

You can install procedural from GitHub with:

# install.packages("pak")
pak::pak("andrewallenbruce/procedural")

🔰 Usage 

library(procedural)

ICD-10-PCS, or the International Classification of Diseases, 10th Revision, Procedure Coding System, is a procedure classification system used to code procedures performed in hospital inpatient health care settings.

Codes 

pcs("0LQV3ZZ") # Medical and Surgical
#> $code
#> [1] "0LQV3ZZ"
#> 
#> $description
#> [1] "Repair Right Foot Tendon, Percutaneous Approach"
